data.name: ReadCsePersonAddress1
data.value: select top(1) IDENTIFIER, CSP_NUMBER, ZDEL_START_DATE, SEND_DATE, SOURCE, STREET_1, STREET_2, CITY, TYPE, WORKER_ID, VERIFIED_DATE, END_DATE, END_CODE, ZDEL_VERIFIED_CODE, LAST_UPDATED_TMST, LAST_UPDATED_BY, [STATE], ZIP_CODE, ZIP4, LOCATION_TYPE, COUNTY from CKT_CSE_PERS_ADDR where (LOCATION_TYPE = 'F') and (CSP_NUMBER = @cspNumber) order by IDENTIFIER desc

data.name: ReadCsePersonAddress2
data.value: select IDENTIFIER, CSP_NUMBER, ZDEL_START_DATE, SEND_DATE, SOURCE, STREET_1, STREET_2, CITY, TYPE, WORKER_ID, VERIFIED_DATE, END_DATE, END_CODE, ZDEL_VERIFIED_CODE, LAST_UPDATED_TMST, LAST_UPDATED_BY, [STATE], ZIP_CODE, ZIP4, LOCATION_TYPE, COUNTY from CKT_CSE_PERS_ADDR where (LOCATION_TYPE = 'D') and ( (END_DATE < @endDate) or ( (END_DATE = @endDate) and (IDENTIFIER < @identifier) ) ) and (CSP_NUMBER = @cspNumber) order by END_DATE desc, IDENTIFIER desc
